org.sbml.jsbml.math.compiler

Class FormulaCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.util.StringTools
      • org.sbml.jsbml.math.compiler.FormulaCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTNode2Compiler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LibSBMLFormulaCompiler

    public class FormulaCompiler
extends StringTools
implements ASTNode2Compiler
    This class creates C-like infix formula Strings that represent the content of ASTNode2s. These can be used to save equations in SBML with older than Level 2.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    $Rev: 2385 $
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger, Victor Kofia
